# An introduction to Microservices using .NET

## A platform management backend application that allows you to add tech platfroms e.g docker and SQL Server and their various commands to a database

## The project included:

- Two .NET Microservices using the REST API pattern
- Dedicated persistence layers for both services
- Deploying the services to Kubernetes cluster
- Employing the API Gateway pattern to route to the services
- Synchronous messaging between services (HTTP & gRPC)
- Asynchronous messaging between services using an Event Bus (RabbitMQ)
